snippet: Bae Sang-moon of South Korea shot a bogey-free, five-under-par 66, giving him a one-shot lead when the second round of the Northern Trust Open was suspended for darkness.
abstract: Bae Sang-moon of South Korea maintains one-shot lead after second round of the Northern Trust Open is suspended for darkness; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Bae Sang-moon of South Korea shot a bogey-free, five-under-par 66, giving him a one-shot lead when the second round of the Northern Trust Open was suspended for darkness.
